results.name: Lightning McQueen
results.title: Crocs Classic Clog Lightning McQueen
results.description:
The Crocs Classic Clog Lightning McQueen is an official collaboration with Disney Pixar's Cars franchise. These Lightning McQueen Crocs pay homage to the movie's lead character, who is voiced by Owen Wilson. The Crocs look is loosely based on the Chevrolet Corvette C1, a racing car produced between 1953 and 1962.

These Lightning McQueen Crocs feature a red foam construction with printed graphics that resemble Lightning McQueen. Ventilation holes on the upper with a sole with grooves add the finishing touch.

The Crocs Classic Clog Lightning McQueen originally released in April of 2021 and retailed for $50, and restocked through the years with the retail price eventually increasing to $60.

Please note: the light up features on the Crocs Classic Clog Lightning McQueen's are not replaceable or rechargeable (and thus may not light up).

results.name: Batman Batmobile
results.title: Crocs Classic Clog Batmobile
results.description:
Step into the iconic world of Gotham City with the Crocs Classic Clog Batmobile. Featuring a playful yet sleek design, these Crocs celebrate one of the most iconic vehicles in cinematic history—the Batmobile. The predominatley black colorway with yellow accents mirrors the mysterious and bold spirit of Batman, and mimics the classic design of the iconic batmobile. While the lightweight, comfortable construction of the Crocs Classic Clog ensures you’re ready for both everyday adventures and heroic missions.

Inspired by the legendary Batmobile, these clogs stand out with their distinct black base complemented by the striking yellow details. Whether you’re a fan of the Batman movies or just looking for a fun, unique addition to your wardrobe, this design allows you to showcase your love for one of the most beloved superheroes, and make a bold style statement.

The Crocs Classic Clog Batmobile, released on September 16, 2024, retailed for $70, offering comfort and flair in one dynamic package. Whether you’re hitting the street or lounging at home, these clogs let you embody the spirit of the Batmobile in style. Black and yellow have never looked so cool!

results.name: Friday The 13th
results.title: Crocs Classic All-Terrain Clog Friday The 13th
results.description:
The Crocs Classic All-Terrain Clog Friday The 13th is a spooky and stylish nod to the iconic horror franchise. This limited edition collaboration brings the thrill of Friday the 13th to the Crocs All-Terrain Clog, featuring a black, cream, and red colorway that evokes the eerie atmosphere of the films. Whether you’re a horror movie fan or just love a unique design, these clogs make a bold statement.

Built with Crocs’ signature Croslite material for lightweight comfort, this model also boasts an adjustable turbo heel strap for added security and stability. The eerie design is complemented by custom Jibbitz charms inspired by Friday the 13th, adding a playful and collectible element to the clogs. Perfect for everyday wear or special Halloween occasions, these clogs seamlessly blend style and comfort with a dose of frightful fun.

Released on September 13, 2024, the Crocs Classic All-Terrain Clog Friday The 13th retailed for $75. This horror-inspired collaboration is perfect for fans of the genre, offering a comfortable, versatile clog that celebrates the spirit of the iconic movie franchise while keeping your feet cozy.

results.name: by Salehe Bembury Niagara
results.title: Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Niagara
results.description:
The Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Niagara clog features a unique collaboration between Crocs and renowned footwear designer Salehe Bembury. The slide has a unique silhouette that is composed of three of Salehe Bembury’s signature fingerprints combined, available in the Niagara colorway.

The Niagara Salehe Bembury Crocs Pollex Clog showcases a "Niagara" color scheme, drawing inspiration from the Serene Gray tones observed at Niagara Falls. With its distinctive concave ridges, this model offers a breathable design, enhanced by intricate cut-out details, and is completed with the addition of a side strap for added functionality. The neutral color scheme is harmoniously paired with a lightweight foam construction, while the concave ridges serve as a practical water siphoning system. The adjustable heel strap proudly showcases dual branding from both Crocs and Salehe Bembury, featuring embossed logos for a distinctive touch.

What our experts love about Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Niagara is its unique design. This collaboration with Salehe Bembury combines elements inspired by nature with innovative design details to create a unique clog that’s not only visually striking, but also comfortable and practical. The clog debuted for $85 on July 20th, 2023.

results.name: by Salehe Bembury Kuwata
results.title: Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Kuwata
results.description:
The Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Salmon Pink is a collaboration show that became one celebrated addition to the brand´s catalog.

Dressed in salmon pink and red, this Pollex clog features an EVA foam upper with clear-cut concave ridges that resemble a fingerprint pattern. Vent holes appear on high-heat areas like the front, midfoot, and ankles. It also features adjustable velcro straps for fitting. Dark red accents the strap holders and the semi-translucent panels on the heel, forefoot, and medial toe.

The Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Salmon Pink was released on 22nd October 2022, with a retail price of $85.

results.name: Naruto Itachi
results.title: Crocs Classic Clog Naruto Itachi
results.description:
The Crocs Classic Clog Naruto Itachi Blue Red pays homage to Itachi Uchiha, a ninja character in the Naruto manga and anime series created by Masashi Kishimoto.

The clog features a dark blue base with cloud-like motifs in red across the upper. It also includes several Jibbitz charms, including a black ninja throwing star and a miniature of the iconic character. Like other Classic Crocs models, this version is made from croslite resin, which is lightweight and durable. Ventilation ports along the sides allow the foot to breathe, while the pivoting heel strap supports a secure fit. A metal tab across the top of the clog displays an emblem associated with Itachi Uchiha.

Our StockX experts like the outsole's traction pattern because it provides grip on various surfaces. The Crocs Classic Clog Naruto Itachi Blue Red was released on June 10, 2024, and retailed for $70.

results.name: Toy Story Buzz Lightyear
results.title: Crocs Classic Clog Toy Story Buzz Lightyear
results.description:
The Crocs Classic Clog Toy Story Buzz Lightyear is part of a partnership between Crocs and Toy Story. It celebrates Buzz Lightyear through a character-specific colorway and imagery.

Like other Crocs, this limited-edition clog features an upper made of durable Croslite foam and a non-slip traction pattern underfoot. The upper boasts four Jibbitz charms, including a spacecraft, Buzz Lightyear’s wings, ‘TO INFINITY AND BEYOND’ in bold yellow letters, and a Buzz Lightyear badge. The area around the Jibbitz charms displays neon green, while the heel strap comes in purple. Other noteworthy details include graphics that read ‘SPACE RANGER,’ ‘LASER,’ and ‘JET EXHAUST DANGER.’

Our StockX experts like the ‘ANDY’ lettering written across the insole. It looks like a child’s handwriting and pays tribute to another character in the movies. The Crocs Classic Clog Toy Story Buzz Lightyear was made available on February 21st, 2024, and sold for $70.

results.name: by Salehe Bembury Como
results.title: Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Como
results.description:
The Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Como is a collaboration between Crocs and Salehe Bembury, an LA-based footwear designer known for his contemporary, eclectic aesthetic and use of luxury materials.

Salehe Bembury updates the recognizable Crocs silhouette and durable resin upper with a mold featuring dramatic, rippling ridges. While the ridges resemble fingerprints or a topographical map, they also serve a function. The concave ripples on the bottom of the shoe increase traction, while the holes on the upper allow the foot to breathe. The shoe boasts an adjustable nylon strap that fits above the heel and can also be removed. Unlike other Crocs, this model does not come with Jibbitz holes on the vamp.

Something our experts love is the closed heel. This is the first Croc produced with a closed heel. Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Como was released on August 17, 2023, and retailed at $85.

results.name: by Salehe Bembury Ube
results.title: Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Ube
results.description:
The Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Ube is a continuation of Salehe Bembury’s innovative Pollex design, this time featuring a unique ube colorway inspired by nature. Known for his use of organic textures and patterns, Bembury transforms the classic Crocs clog into a modern, fashion-forward piece. The ube color, a rich purple hue, adds a bold and distinctive look to the already iconic silhouette.

The Pollex Clog features strategically placed ventilation ports and ridged textures, enhancing breathability and grip for all-day comfort. The ergonomic design, with its bold grooves and contoured fit, ensures maximum comfort and functionality. The unique ube colorway adds a playful yet sophisticated touch, making this collaboration a must-have for fans of Salehe Bembury’s design language and those seeking a unique addition to their footwear rotation.

Released on August 8, 2024, the Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Ube retailed for $85. This limited-edition clog continues to push the boundaries of Crocs design, offering both style and comfort with a unique colorway that’s sure to stand out.

results.name: SpongeBob SquarePants Patrick Star
results.title: Crocs Classic Clog SpongeBob SquarePants Patrick Star
results.description:
The Crocs Classic Clog SpongeBob SquarePants Patrick Star updates the Crocs silhouette with motifs and colors inspired by the animated starfish from the SpongeBob SquarePants universe.

The upper is made of a lightweight and water-friendly material with ventilation ports that increase breathability. The top of the shoe comes in a light pink that mimics Patrick’s skin tone, while the underfoot area features a pattern that matches his shorts. This Croc includes several Patrick-themed Jibbitz charms, including a model of the character, a coconut, a jar of mayonnaise, and a tube of SPF 45 sunscreen. The adjustable ankle strap displays the quote "is mayonnaise an instrument?" while Patrick’s face graces the interior footbed

Our experts at StockX like the light traction pattern underfoot, which helps the shoe grip the ground. The Crocs Classic Clog SpongeBob SquarePants Patrick Star was released on May 22, 2024, and retailed at $70.

results.name: by Salehe Bembury Horchata
results.title: Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Horchata
results.description:
When it comes to redefining comfort with style, the Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury did just that, dropping the Horchata colorway on June 15, 2023. Fusing contemporary fashion with relaxed footwear.

The Horchata colorway reflects an earthy vibe, drenched in a calming shade that screams understated cool. The distinctive silhouette of the clog meets an innovative, grippy outsole, marrying function with fashion. Bembury's signature design elements elevate the aesthetic, proving that comfort doesn't mean compromising on style.

The Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury in Horchata released on June 15, 2023, for a retail price of $85, ensuring that trendsetters could kick back in style without breaking the bank.

results.name: Black
results.title: Crocs Classic Clog Black
results.description:
Since its debut, Crocs Classic Clog Black has become popular unisex footwear in the Crocs series.

The Classic Clog is produced from croslite material covered in style code 10001BLK. This item is covered with a black colorway, with enough perforations at the Crocs' upper and sides of the toes that help in the breathability as well as the drainage of excess water or sand from the inside of the Croc. The design features an extended heel strap for comfortability while in movement.

Crocs Classic Clog Black was initially released on July 15, 2022, at a retail price of $50.

results.name: by Salehe Bembury Yoke
results.title: Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Yoke
results.description:
The Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Yoke is part of a collaboration between Crocs and Salehe Bembury, a US-based footwear designer known for his futuristic, functional designs.

The upper is made of durable Croslite resin and features concave ridges and wavy patterns. These ridges and patterns were inspired by three different sets of fingerprints and provide multi-directional traction underfoot. Outsole pods also provide addition traction and add durability. The Croc has two adjustable heel straps that can also be removed depending on the needs of the wearer. Holes on high-heat areas of the foot provide an airy feel and also allow water to drain from the shoe.

Our experts at StockX like the vibrant yellow colorway called "Yoke" because it only has one tone and draws attention to the design. The Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Yoke was released on November 9th, 2023, and retailed at $85.

results.name: by Salehe Bembury Tide
results.title: Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Tide
results.description:
The Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Tide is a product of the collaboration between the American footwear company Crocs and footwear designer Salehe Bembury.​
​​
​This product features two adjustable and removable heel straps constructed out of nylon, "Fingerprint" concave ridges for multi-directional traction, outsole pods designed to take abrasion, ridges on its upper side to enable water to channel off the shoe, and holes on its upper to improve its breathability.​
​​
​The Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Tide was released on 22nd September 2022. At the time of its release, this Salehe Bembury Tide colorway model had a retail price of $85.

results.name: Naruto Shippuden Kakashi
results.title: Crocs Classic Clog Naruto Shippuden Kakashi
results.description:
The Crocs Classic Clog Naruto Shippuden Kakashi is part of a collaboration between Crocs and Naruto Shippuden, a Japanese manga and anime series created by Masashi Kishimoto.

This slip-on shoe pays tribute to Kakashi Hatake, a ninja and protagonist in the series, through colors and motifs. For example, the clog boasts a green base, which symbolizes Kakashi Hatake’s uniform. Several Jibbitz charms can be found on the upper, including a ninja star, a replica of the ninja’s face, a red rectangle featuring fighting characters, a weapon, and a cat-like mask. Instead of a traditional heel strap, this Croc comes with a padded strap that resembles bomber jacket material. There is also a small pouch, which can be attached to the heel strap with a snap.

Our StockX experts like the enhanced traction on the underside of the shoe, which comes in contrasting navy. The Crocs Classic Clog Naruto Shippuden Kakashi was released on February 27th, 2024, and retailed at $70.

results.name: SpongeBob SquarePants
results.title: Crocs Classic Clog SpongeBob SquarePants
results.description:
The Crocs Classic Clog SpongeBob SquarePants features a yellow upper and heel strap, accented by SpongeBob SquarePants’ signature yellow hands, white sleeves, and red necktie.

Originating in 1999, SpongeBob SquarePants is Nickelodeon’s most popular animated series, which has garnered fans worldwide since its debut. Crocs is an American brand known for their signature molded shoe's comfort, practicality, and unique features. Crocs is also known for the numerous variations iterated of its Classic Clog, which the brand reimagines in a myriad of ways. SpongeBob’s face accents the heel strap on one side, while Crocs branding adorns the other side. The midsole features a brown and black design in the style of SpongeBob’s brown pants and black belt. A yellow outsole completes the SpongeBob aesthetic.

In our opinion, the best feature of the Classic Clog SpongeBob is SpongeBob’s hands, which are three-dimensional and adorn the shoe like Jibbitz. The Crocs Classic Clog SpongeBob SquarePants released on May 22, 2024, and retailed at $70.

results.name: by Salehe Bembury Sasquatch
results.title: Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Sasquatch
results.description:
Since its release, Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Sasquatch remains of the highest-selling variants in the Crocs catalog.

The construction of Pollex Clog mainly utilizes croslite material. These Crocs come in an attractive sasquatch black colorway and feature a heel attached to the optional sport mode for great fitting. The upper part is perforated to enhance its breathability and allow the shedding of water and other particles, such as debris, from inside the Crocs.

The Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Sasquatch was released on September 22, 2022. At the time of the release, its retail price was $85.

results.name: Marvel Spider-Man
results.title: Crocs Classic All-Terrain Clog Marvel Spider-Man
results.description:
The Crocs Classic All-Terrain Clog Marvel Spider-Man is an iconic silhouette that is playful in design and durable in construction.

The Marvel Spider-Man x Crocs Classic All-Terrain Clog features an upper of red Croslite crisscrossed with black lines to look like a spider web. This slip-on shoe features a red Croslite heel strap sporting black tabs with graphics. An insole of black Croslite sports Crocs branding and is perforated for breathability and to keep your foot from slipping. Spider-Man's face appears at the heel-strap joints, and a large black spider is imprinted on the toe box among the perforations. The toe box also features Spider-Man cartoon graphics.

What we enjoy most about this classic croc is its durable sole unit. A black Croslite outsole has durable pods lining the outer rim and herringbone-like lugs for traction under the heel and forefoot. The Crocs Classic All-Terrain Clog Marvel Spider-Man was released on May 24, 2023, for $85 retail.

results.name: Diplo Take a Walk on the Weird Side
results.title: Crocs Classic Clog Diplo Take a Walk on the Weird Side
results.description:
Since its debut, Crocs Classic Clog Diplo Take a Walk on the Weird Side remains one of the highest-selling variants of the Crocs catalog.

The Crocs is made from Croslite (TM) materials and comes in a multicolor colorway. The Crocs are buoyant and lightweight, with water-friendly features. Apart from these, the Classic Clog has ventilation ports that help in the shedding of sand particles and water. In addition to this, these ports of the Crocs enhance breathability. The design of the Crocs becomes complete with the pivoted heel strap.

The Crocs Classic Clog Diplo Take a Walk on the Weird Side was first released on June 8, 2021, at a price of $70.
